    "description": "<p>Combat servitors are armed with highly effective combat weaponry and programmed with basic weapon routines to use them. These lobotomised cyborgs serve as expendable shock troops and guardians, executing their programming with mechanical precision and no regard for self-preservation.</p><p><strong>Source:</strong> Dark Heresy Core Rulebook, p. 338</p>",
